Name: Dogolrax
About the game: You awake on an unknown planet with amnesia. What are those horrific monsters? Who are these mysterious priestesses? You will explore a bizarre, grotesque and captivating world filled with surprises. Inspired by cult classics such as 'Another World/Out of this World', 'Flashback' and other cult classics, Dogolrax aims to surprise you in ways few games have before by introducing constant changes in gameplay, environment, monsters, dialog and plot twists. Expect the unexpected plus a good dose of humor, gore, tease and varied gameplay.
